				<div class="comment-author vcard">
			<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/blavatar/87dfc96850e4e3abd4d0df855c3a1cd9?s=40' class='avatar avatar-40' height='40' width='40' />			<cite class="fn"><a href='http://fightcopyrighttrolls.com/2014/06/25/copyright-troll-malibu-media-targets-a-business-but-fails-to-timely-serve-it/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Copyright troll Malibu Media targets a business, but fails to timely serve it | Fight Copyright Trolls</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>		</div>
		
